text: Jung Yoo-jin (born February 19, 1989), also known as Eugene Jung, is a South Korean model and actress. She started her career as a model at YG Entertainment. She is known for her roles in Korean dramas, such as Heard It Through the Grapevine (2015), Moorim School and W.
